abstract: He won’t be on the debate stage next week. But he says his campaign continues, “debate or not.”
snippet: He won’t be on the debate stage next week. But he says his campaign continues, “debate or not.”
lead_paragraph: In less than six hours, we will know who’s officially made the cut for next week’s Democratic primary debate.

abstract: He was a follower of the fringe Black Hebrew Israelite movement, which has expressed hostility to Jews, officials said.
snippet: He was a follower of the fringe Black Hebrew Israelite movement, which has expressed hostility to Jews, officials said.
lead_paragraph: After first saying that a deadly rampage at a New Jersey kosher market was random, the authorities disclosed on Wednesday that one of the two attackers had published anti-Semitic posts online and had, in fact, targeted the site.

abstract: The Black Hebrew Israelites have been labeled a hate group. The suspect wrote anti-Semitic and anti-police posts, an official said.
snippet: The Black Hebrew Israelites have been labeled a hate group. The suspect wrote anti-Semitic and anti-police posts, an official said.
lead_paragraph: An assailant involved in the prolonged firefight in Jersey City, N.J., that left six people dead, including one police officer, was linked on Wednesday to the Black Hebrew Israelite movement, and had published anti-Semitic posts online, a law enforcement official said.

abstract: The presidential candidates need to stop demurring and fully reject Trump’s approach.
snippet: The presidential candidates need to stop demurring and fully reject Trump’s approach.
lead_paragraph: When it comes to trade policy with China, the Democratic presidential candidates face a conundrum. They don’t want to sign onto President Trump’s endless, chaotic, pain-over-gain trade war, yet they don’t want to appear weak or appeasing of China’s trade practices.

abstract: He cleared a final polling hurdle to join six other candidates, ensuring there won’t be an all-white debate.
snippet: He cleared a final polling hurdle to join six other candidates, ensuring there won’t be an all-white debate.
lead_paragraph: The entrepreneur Andrew Yang has qualified for next week’s Democratic debate, bringing the lineup to seven and ensuring that the candidates onstage will not all be white, though the lineup still does not include any black or Latino candidates.

abstract: Many of the artist’s works have traveled from around the world to a major show at the Louvre. But many more remain in Italy, in cities and small towns alike.
snippet: Many of the artist’s works have traveled from around the world to a major show at the Louvre. But many more remain in Italy, in cities and small towns alike.
lead_paragraph: VINCI, Italy — In his biography of Leonardo da Vinci, written 30 years after the artist’s death in 1519, Giorgio Vasari said Leonardo had “such a power of intellect that whatever he turned his mind to, he made himself master of with ease.”

abstract: Developers are clamoring for storefront space as they seek to provide one-of-a-kind experiences for shoppers.
snippet: Developers are clamoring for storefront space as they seek to provide one-of-a-kind experiences for shoppers.
lead_paragraph: Five years ago, Eli Gindi, a New York businessman, learned that part of the Showcase Mall on the Las Vegas Strip was up for sale. His interest piqued, he informally toured the property a few weeks later while in town for business.
